      "description": "Initial public release.\n\n- Insert footnotes at the cursor with an auto-numbered label; write the text in a popup without leaving your place\n- Click any footnote number (Live Preview or Reading view) to edit it in place\n- Edit footnote at cursor command for a keyboard-only flow\n- Delete a footnote everywhere (definition + all references) in one undo step\n- Multi-line footnotes supported\n- Settings: auto-numbering toggle, click-to-edit toggle",
